com.tozny.e3db

Interface EAKInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalEAKInfo

    public interface EAKInfo
    An encrypted key, intended for a given client, that can be used to encrypt or decrypt documents.

    Consider using the LocalEAKInfo implementation.
